============================================================
                        PHOTOMOSAIC
============================================================

An open-source photomosaic renderer.

This project is available at:
http://github.com/jpg18/photomosaic/

Contact: jeffrey.p.gill@gmail.com

Copyright (c) 2011, Jeffrey P. Gill


Antipole Tree Data Structure and Search Algorithms
============================================================
This software contains an implementation of the antipole
tree data structure and search algorithms presented in:

D. Cantone, A. Ferro, A. Pulvirenti, D. R. Recupero, and
D. Shasha. Antipole tree indexing to support range search
and k-nearest neighbor search in metric spaces. IEEE
Transactions on Knowledge and Data Engineering, 17(4):535-
550, 2005.


Photomosaic Construction Algorithm
============================================================
This software is based on an algorithm for building
photomosaics presented in:

G. di Blasi, G. Gallo, and M. P. Petralia. Smart ideas for
photomosaic rendering. In Proceedings of Eurographics
Italian Chapter Conference, pp. 267-272, 2006.

============================================================

